<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.8.3">
<l>eṉnāṉ ceykēṉ yārē kaḷaika ṇeṉṉaiyeṉ ceykiṉṟā</l>
<l>yuṉṉā lallāl yāva rālu moṉṟuṅ kuṟaivēṇṭēṉ</l>
<l>kaṉṉār matiḷcūḻ kuṭantaik kiṭantā yaṭiyē ṉaruvāḻnāḷ</l>
<l>ceṉṉā ḷennā ḷannā ḷuṉṟāḷ piṭittē celakkāṇē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What can I do? Who [is there as] a support? What do you do to me?</l>
<l>I don’t have any request from anyone but from you.</l>
<l>You who lie in Kuṭantai surrounded by well-crafted walls, the difficult days I, [your] servant live,</l>
<l>whichever day of the going days, see that day go [me] gripping your feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
